    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Low-Resource Translation Notebook\\n\",\"**NLP Project 68 of 100** — Evaluate translation quality for underrepresented languages.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess,sys,importlib\\nfor pkg in ['transformers','torch','sacrebleu']:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,'-m','pip','install','-q',pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"from transformers import pipeline\\nimport torch, sacrebleu\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\ndevice = 0 if torch.cuda.is_available() else -1\\nprint(f'Device: {\\\"GPU\\\" if device==0 else \\\"CPU\\\"}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"# Test English → low-resource language pairs\\n# Using Helsinki-NLP models (available for many language pairs)\\npairs = [\\n    ('en','sw','Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-swc','Swahili'),  # Swahili\\n    ('en','fi','Helsinki-NLP/opus-mt-en-fi','Finnish'),\\n]\\n\\ntest_sentences = ['Hello, how are you today?','Machine learning is transforming healthcare.','The weather is nice.']\\n\\nfor src, tgt, model_name, lang_name in pairs:\\n    try:\\n        translator = pipeline('translation', model=model_name, device=device)\\n        print(f'\\\\n=== English → {lang_name} ===')\\n        for sent in test_sentences:\\n            result = translator(sent)\\n            print(f'  EN: {sent}')\\n            print(f'  {lang_name}: {result[0][\\\"translation_text\\\"]}')\\n    except Exception as e:\\n        print(f'\\\\n=== English → {lang_name} ===')\\n        print(f'  Model not available: {e}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Low-resource languages have fewer parallel corpora** for training.\\n\",\"- **Translation quality varies significantly** between well-resourced and underrepresented languages.\\n\",\"- **NLLB-200 (Meta) covers 200 languages** and is the best option for low-resource pairs.\\n\",\"- **For production, use human evaluation** alongside BLEU for low-resource languages.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
